text: Stephen Butcher may refer to: *Stephen Butcher (Royal Marine) (1904-2005), English serviceman; one of UK's last 11 veterans of World War I *Stephen Butcher (director) (born 1946), English television director of Eastenders *Stephen Butcher (Sudbury) (born 1953), Canadian politician *Stephen Butcher (footballer) (born 1994), English footballer ==See also== *Butcher (disambiguation)
title: Stephen Butcher
